reporting-org.narrative: New Zealand Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade

description.narrative: The activity will create a sustainable domestic milk supply in Fiji that includes viable smallholder dairy farmers. To achieve this the activity will: • Develop a Fiji Dairy Industry database • Develop a Dairy Industry Strategy • Establish a Milk Supply and Purchase Agreement and milk quality assurance system • Develop an extension system • Establish a training farm; and • Upgrade milk collection centres
